the `ENTRY_USAGE_OVERESTIMATE` in https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/commit/9dcef47e4d52b15ffe88be7ddf5ea626121e5f0d is a bit much and two transaction are being added to `disconnectpool` for the first  test that check that its big enough for one transaction.
